In your works,you frequenctly encounter some proplems,for instances,your text file have continuous character '\n' or some other special symbols
you should substitute the character with goal string or character,the command as follow must be used.
take a "a.txt" for example,some blank line in your file,you should use below command to do what you want.
$tr -s '\n' new.txt |less or tr -s '\n' new.txt >new1.txt
$cat format.txt |tr -s '\n' >new.txt  #if above no work,try this command again.

####
if you want to see whole statue on you top,you should try command "htop" or "ps -fx".
